tspan.tspan: They are UK’s and Europe’s leading independent rail and coach
platform. They sell tickets on behalf of more than 140 rail and
coach companies, offering their customers millions of travel
options across 36 countries. The technology company had a
simple mission - to bring together all rail, coach and other travel
services into one simple experience so customers can get the
best prices and smart, real-time travel information on the go.

text.tspan: Please hear David Jack who was the ex CIO of Trainline talk
about some of his business challenges before engaging us 12
The video is from 10 years ago and around the same time, we
collated all our experiences to write the book on Continuous
Delivery, which is now a seminal work of software delivery
The decade-long relationship between Trainline and
Thoughtworks has been a collaboration involving progressive
changes supporting different parts of their organization. These
include the call centre system, website, backend web services,
optimization for mobile and efficient data processing. Please see
the approach we took to help them become successful.
